videos.headline: Auburn RB throws TD pass vs. Georgia
videos.description: Auburn runs the wildcat offense and running back JaTarvious Whitlow throws to John Shenker for a 9-yard touchdown to take the lead over Georgia.

videos.headline: Fromm hits Simmons for TD to retake lead
videos.description: Jake Fromm drops back and finds Tyler Simmons in the end zone from 14 yards away to put Georgia ahead vs. Auburn.

videos.headline: Fromm hits Godwin in stride for 38-yard TD
videos.description: Jake Fromm connects with Terry Godwin over the middle for a 38-yard score near the end of the 1st half vs. Auburn.

videos.headline: Fromm, Georgia on top of Auburn at the half
videos.description: After Auburn uses some trickery to get in the end zone, Jake Fromm tosses a pair of touchdowns to give Georgia a 20-10 lead.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Fromm, Georgia on top of Auburn at the half) 2018/11/10 ESHEET SOTFull

videos.headline: Fromm picked off by Auburn
videos.description: Jake Fromm's pass is intercepted by Jamel Dean to give Auburn the ball back early in the 2nd half.

videos.headline: Fromm, Swift lead Georgia past Auburn
videos.description: Jake Fromm throws a pair of touchdowns in the first half and D'Andre Swift rushes for 186 yards and a score in a 27-10 win over Auburn.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Fromm, Swift lead Georgia past Auburn) 2018/11/10 ESHEET SOTFull

videos.headline: Swift on Georgia's O-line: 'I can't do nothing without them'
videos.description: D'Andre Swift says Georgia's offensive line allowed him to excel in the rushing and passing game in a rivalry win vs. Auburn.

videos.headline: Smart: Georgia still a 'work in progress' after beating Auburn
videos.description: Kirby Smart says Georgia's offense was clicking vs. Auburn, but the Bulldogs still have room for improvement moving forward.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Interview (Smart: Georgia still a 'work in progress' after beating Auburn) 2018/11/10
